#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Intangiriro"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmagnifier; is a screen magnifier by the KDE community. It can be used to "
"magnify a part of the screen. This application can be useful to various "
"people: People with low vision can use this application to magnify a part of "
"the screen which they are unable to view clearly, artists can use this "
"application to zoom into the graphics they produce and verify it at the "
"pixel level, image-processing researchers can use this application to zoom "
"into images and study them closely. Other than these, &kmagnifier; can be "
"used for various other purposes &eg; is possible to use the application for "
"grabbing a portion of the screen and saving it to the disk (with an option "
"of zooming the screen captured)."
msgstr ""
"&kmag; ni A Mugaragaza ya:  i ( &kde; ) . Byakoreshejwe Kuri Gutubura A "
"Inzira %s Bya i Mugaragaza . Porogaramu Kuri Abantu : Na: hasi Koresha iyi "
"Porogaramu Kuri Gutubura A Inzira %s Bya i Mugaragaza Kuri Reba , Koresha "
"iyi Porogaramu Kuri Ihindurangano i Ibishushanyo na Gusuzuma: Ku i urwego , "
"Ishusho - Inonosora Koresha iyi Porogaramu Kuri Ihindurangano Ishusho na . , "
"&kmag; Byakoreshejwe ya:  Ikindi Impamvu &eg; ni Kuri Koresha i Porogaramu "
"ya:  A Bya i Mugaragaza na Mu kubika Kuri i Disiki%1 ( Na: Ihitamo Bya i "
"Mugaragaza ) . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmagnifier; is a very powerful application with new features being added "
"all the time. It is optimized for use on low processing power machines."
msgstr ""
"&kmag; ni A Porogaramu Na: Gishya Ibiranga Kyongewe Byose i Igihe . ni "
"Cyuzuye ya:  Koresha ku hasi Inonosora UMWIKUBE . "

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:122
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kmagnifier;"
msgstr "ikoresha"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:125
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screen shot of &kmagnifier;"
msgstr "A Mugaragaza Bya &kmag; "

#. Tag: phrase
